3644	  \(\Sigma\,\iota,\ \iota \to \mathrm{Opens}(X)\) over which the section {\v C}ech complex is built.
3645	  The cover system bundles:
3646	  \begin{enumerate}
3647	  \item a basis \(\mathcal{B} \subseteq \mathrm{Opens}(X)\) for the topology;
3648	  \item a set \(\mathrm{Cov}\) of admissible coverings, each a \(\mathrm{CovDatum}\);
3649	  \item \emph{faces-in-basis} (\(\mathrm{faces\_mem}\)): for every covering in \(\mathrm{Cov}\) every
3650	    finite intersection \(U_{i_0 \ldots i_p}\) of its opens lies in \(\mathcal{B}\) (condition (1) of
3651	    Lemma~\ref{lem:cech_to_cohomology_on_basis});
3652	  \item \emph{section surjectivity} (\(\mathrm{surj\_of\_vanishing}\)): for every \(V \in \mathcal{B}\)
3653	    and every short exact sequence \(S : 0 \to S_1 \to S_2 \to S_3 \to 0\) of \(\mathcal{O}_X\)-modules
3654	    whose left term \(S_1\) has vanishing positive {\v C}ech cohomology over the coverings of \(V\) in
3655	    \(\mathrm{Cov}\), the section map \(S_2(V) \to S_3(V)\) is surjective;
3656	  \item \emph{injective acyclicity} (\(\mathrm{injective\_acyclic}\)): for every injective
3657	    \(\mathcal{O}_X\)-module \(\mathcal{I}\) and every covering \(\mathcal{U} \in \mathrm{Cov}\) the
3658	    positive-degree {\v C}ech cohomology vanishes, \(\check{H}^p(\mathcal{U}, \mathcal{I}) = 0\) for
3659	    all \(p > 0\).
3660	  \end{enumerate}
3661	  Unlike a bare combinatorial record, the structure carries two sheaf-theoretic ({\v C}ech-cohomology)
