  Every injective \(\mathcal{O}_X\)-module \(\mathcal{I}\) has vanishing positive-degree {\v C}ech
  cohomology over the standard covers of the affine: \(\check{H}^p(\mathcal{U}, \mathcal{I}) = 0\) for
  every standard cover \(\mathcal{U} \in \mathrm{Cov}\) and every \(p > 0\). This discharges the
